---

<Layout title="Scheidler Medical">
    <main class="grid">
        <Hero />
        <section class="snap-y">
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-y-4 sm:gap-y-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500 to-indigo-600 px-4 py-8 sm:p-12">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
                    <img src="/doctor.svg" alt="Doctor caring for patient" height={800} width={800} />
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col p-4 sm:p-12 gap-y-8 sm:gap-y-12">
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-50 sm:text-4xl">
                            Accepting New Patients
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-100">
                            Scheidler Medical Preferred offers comprehensive primary care services for the entire
                            family, including preventative care, minor surgery, and acute illness care. Our scheduling
                            services typically allow you to make an appointment within a few days.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Our Care Stands Out</h2>
                        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-100">
                            We want to solve and treat our patientâ€™s medical ailments whether they be physical or
                            mental. Our primary advantage is that we offer comprehensive medical care. Most primary care
                            physicians refer out for many of the services we offer. Our core services include primary
                            care, addiction treatment, geriatrics, weight loss, minor surgeries, XRAY, osteopathic
                            manipulative treatment, medical spa, counseling services, and blood testing on-site.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="snap-y">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-y-12 px-6 sm:px-12 py-4 sm:py-20">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Services</h2>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 max-w-3xl text-center">
                        Scheidler Medical Preferred is committed to providing personalized, lifelong care for your
                        entire family. Below are just a few of the common medical services we make available to our
                        patients.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 [&>*:nth-child(odd)]:bg-yellow-100 [&>*:nth-child(odd)]:text-yellow-900 [&>*:nth-child(even)]:bg-green-100 [&>*:nth-child(even)]:text-green-900"
                >
                    {
                        services.map((service) => (
                            <div class="flex flex-col justify-around items-center h-48 w-80 sm:w-56 xl:w-72 shadow-md rounded-xl p-8" transition:name="service-card">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-center">
                                    {service.name}
                                </h3>
                            </div>
                        ))
                    }
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
